<div class="centerbox center">
  <h2>You're doing great work.</h2>
  <p>Breaking down walls between languages and cultures is important stuff. <br> You deserve credit for it!</p>
  <br>
  <p>Here's how to sign in:</p>
    <li><b><a href="#" id="sign-in">Sign in with Heyu.</a></li>
    <li>Not a member? <%= link_to "Join for free", '/sign_up' %>.</li>
    <!--- COMING SOON! :) <li><%= link_to "Sign in with Twitter", "/auth/twitter" %>.</li> -->
    <br>
      <%= form_tag sessions_path do %>
      <p>
        <%= label_tag :username %>
        <%= text_field_tag :name, params[:name] %>
      </p>
      <p>
        <%= label_tag :password %>
        <%= password_field_tag :password %>
      </p>
      <p class="button"><%= submit_tag "Sign in" %></p>
    <% end %>
</div>